'''李·巴里·卡特摩尔'''（{{lang-en|'''Lee Barry Cattermole'''}}，{{bd|1988年|3月21日|catidx=Cattermole, Lee}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[蒂斯塞德|蒂斯塞德]]（Teesside）的[[蒂斯河畔斯托克|蒂斯河畔斯托克]]（Stockton-on-Tees），是一名[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，現時已退役。

==生平==
===米杜士堡===
卡特摩尔出身於於[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]青訓系統<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensSeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/2006/WCScout_Ruiz.aspx |title=Boro grow from within |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]] |date=2006-03-30 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516004450/https://www.thefa.com/England/MensSeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/2006/WCScout_Ruiz.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，於2006年1月2日在東北部[[泰恩-蒂斯打吡|泰恩-蒂斯打吡]]（Tyne-Tees derby）對[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]在[[英超|英超]]處子上陣，踢足全場而雙方2-2平手終場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4562602.stm |title=Newcastle 2-2 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-01-02 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103749/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4562602.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。4月2日作客對[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]一箭定江山兼取得個人首個英超入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4853690.stm |title=Man City 0-1 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-04-02 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103754/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4853690.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。5月7日年僅18歲的卡特摩尔成為米杜士堡歷來最年輕的[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，帶領球隊在煞科戰作客對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]，比賽餘下5分鐘，年達39歲的[[哥連·谷巴|哥連·谷巴]]（Colin Cooper）後補上陣，進行退役前最後一次露面，卡特摩尔自動將隊長臂章交給哥連·谷巴作為對老隊員的尊敬，而這場亦是領隊[[史提夫·麥卡倫|麥卡倫]]轉教[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]前最後一場在[[英超|英超]]領導米杜士堡，雖然以0-1落敗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4957456.stm |title=Fulham 1-0 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-07 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103758/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4957456.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但這場比賽米杜士堡的正副選合共16名隊員中有15名在[[河畔球場|河畔球場]]（Riverside Stadium）約30[[英里|英里]]內出生，卡特摩尔是其中之一<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensSeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/2006/England_McClaren.aspx |title=McClaren's legacy |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]] |date=2006-05-09 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515234229/https://www.thefa.com/England/MensSeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/2006/England_McClaren.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。5月10日[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]決賽對[[西維爾足球會|西維爾]]，卡特摩尔於比賽末段入替[[马克·维杜卡|維杜卡]]，米杜士堡以0-4落敗屈居亞軍<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/4751467.stm |title=Middlesbrough 0-4 Sevilla |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-10 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2014-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140515023056/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/4751467.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2006年8月23日米杜士堡主2-1擊敗[[英超|英超]]衛冕冠軍[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]，卡特摩尔於下半場後補入替<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/5266168.stm |title=Middlesbrough 2-1 Chelsea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-23 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225181258/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/5266168.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，雖然[[足踝|足踝]]剛傷癒，隨即與對方中場鐵漢[[克洛德·馬克萊萊|馬基利尼]]硬碰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11680_2388336,00.html |title=Fiery Catt won't change |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-08-31 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041259/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11680_2388336,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其勇猛踢法使他在上季僅24場比賽已累計接到7面[[黃牌|黃牌]]。10月20日卡特摩尔續約四年直到2010年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/middlesbrough/6070030.stm |title=Cattermole signs new deal at Boro |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-10-20 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103823/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/middlesbrough/6070030.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2007年1月13日作客對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]，卡特摩尔完半場前扳平1-1，最終米杜士堡反勝3-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6236697.stm |title=Charlton 1-3 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-13 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6236697.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。3月10日在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]半準決賽主場對[[曼联足球俱乐部|曼聯]]，卡特摩尔再於完半場前扳平1-1，曼聯僅憑[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|基斯坦奴·朗拿度]]的[[十二碼|十二碼]]追平2-2<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6415073.stm |title=Middlesbrough 2-2 Man Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-10 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103837/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6415073.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，重賽作客再失[[十二碼|十二碼]]而負0-1被淘汰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6461727.stm |title=Man Utd 1-0 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-19 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103840/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6461727.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在他的首個完整[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|球季]]中，於39場比賽中累積多達12面[[黃牌|黃牌]]。

2007年8月18日作客對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]，卡特摩尔完場前兩分鐘射入鎖定2-1勝局，為球隊帶來[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|新球季]]的首場勝仗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6941857.stm |title=Fulham 1-2 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-18 |accessdate=2009-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6941857.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但在新任領隊[[加雷思·索斯盖特|修夫基]]（Gareth Southgate）麾下卻不獲重用，整季只有28場上陣機會，大部分更是於比賽末段才獲派後補上場，沒有取得入球卻仍有7面[[黃牌|黃牌]]。

===韋根===
2008年7月29日卡特摩尔轉投[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]，身價據稱達到350萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約三年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/7521234.stm |title=Cattermole wraps up move to Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-29 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103850/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/7521234.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他於8月16日首次披甲作客出戰[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，以1-2敗陣而回<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7551169.stm |title=West Ham 2-1 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-16 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209230634/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7551169.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。踢法勇悍的卡特摩尔在第四場為韋根上陣主場對[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]時領取個人在[[英超|英超]]首面[[紅牌|紅牌]]，於完場前5分鐘侵犯[[特穆·泰尼奥|泰尼奥]]接獲第二面[[黃牌|黃牌]]被驅逐離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7601901.stm |title=Wigan 1-1 Sunderland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-13 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103901/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7601901.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。停賽後復出首場比賽，於9月24日在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]第三圈作客對[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]，卡特摩尔先拔頭籌兼射入加盟以來首個入球，協助球隊輕勝4-1過關<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7626823.stm |title=Ipswich 1-4 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-24 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2020-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621230038/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7626823.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。 

2008年11月15日深夜卡特摩尔與兩名友人在[[米德爾斯伯勒|米德爾斯伯勒]]（Middlesbrough）一家[[夜總會|夜總會]]外因妨害公共秩序（public order offence）被捕，其後被罰定額罰款了事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/7733468.stm |title=Player fined for disorder offence |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103911/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/7733468.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。12月13日主場3-0擊敗[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]，卡特摩尔射入「埋齋」的一球而在[[英超|英超]]「開齋」，這場敗仗直接導致對方領隊[[保罗·因斯|保罗·因斯]]被炒<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7763502.stm |title=Wigan 3-0 Blackburn |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-13 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103916/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7763502.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

卡特摩尔在[[新年|新年]]前已累計6[[黃牌|黃]]1[[紅牌|紅]]，其紀律比另一員中場悍將[[威尔森·帕拉西奥斯|柏拉西奧斯]]的7面黃牌還要差，他過勇的攔截令人聞風喪膽；先在2008年11月15日於開賽後僅15分鐘即因一次50-50的硬朗攔截將[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]中場硬漢[[乔伊·巴顿|祖爾·巴頓]]踢傷離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7711309.stm |title=Newcastle 2-2 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-15 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610052618/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7711309.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，祖爾·巴頓因而缺陣長達兩個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7733109.stm |title=Barton ruled out for two months |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2009-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227045436/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7733109.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；在[[节礼日|拆禮物日]]再戰紐卡素，卡特摩尔上半場38分鐘的一記攔截又踢斷[[哈比布·貝耶|比耶]]（Habib Beye）的[[足踝|足踝]]韌帶，令後者養傷長達三個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/premierleague/newcastle/4679195/Newcastles-Habib-Beye-eyes-early-return-to-help-fight-in-relegation-battle.html |title=Newcastle's Habib Beye eyes early return to help fight in relegation battle |publisher=Telegraph.co.uk |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archive-date=2009-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313192612/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/premierleague/newcastle/4679195/Newcastles-Habib-Beye-eyes-early-return-to-help-fight-in-relegation-battle.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；2009年2月21日重返[[河畔球場|河畔球場]]對母會[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]，卡特摩尔全場被主場球迷喝倒彩，於上半場23分鐘與對方防守中場[[迪迪埃·迪加德|迪加特]]（Didier Digard）碰撞後，迪加特需用擔架抬離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7885827.stm |title=Middlesbrough 0-0 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103936/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7885827.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，迪加特雙腳均受傷，需缺席三個月而提早「收咧」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/middlesbrough/7906611.stm |title=Middlesbrough hit by Digard blow |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-23 |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103941/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/middlesbrough/7906611.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；2009年3月4日主場對爭逐[[英超|英超]]第七位的[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，球證出示兩[[紅牌|紅]]八[[黃牌|黃]]以控制雙方過激的球員，下半場[[盧卡斯·尼爾|尼爾]]向卡特摩尔作出一記恐怖的攔截而僅被罰[[黃牌|黃牌]]，數分鐘後卡特摩尔向[[斯科特·帕克|柏加]]（Scott Parker）作出一次魯莽攔截而被直接罰[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7908464.stm |title=Wigan 0-1 West Ham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-04 |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103946/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7908464.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，是本季領取的第二面紅牌而需停賽4場，加上累積9面黃牌再加停兩場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/article2298922.ece?OTC-RSS&ATTR=Football |title=Seven and hell for bad-boy Lee |publisher=thesun.co.uk |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archive-date=2009-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090308163046/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/article2298922.ece?OTC-RSS&ATTR=Football |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年7月10日已轉投[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]的[[斯蒂夫·布鲁斯|布魯士]]出價要求收購卡特摩尔增強中場截擊力，但韋根以他為「非賣品」而予回絕<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/8144737.stm |title=Sunderland fail in Cattermole bid |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-10 |accessdate=2009-07-11 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103955/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/8144737.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===新特蘭===
2009年8月12日卡特摩尔以600萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]成功轉投[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]，簽約四年，與布魯士重聚<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/8198227.stm |title=Sunderland swoop for Cattermole |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-12 |accessdate=2009-08-13 |archive-date=2009-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090815155417/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/8198227.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2010–11賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2010/11年度英超球季]]開始前，領隊[[斯蒂夫·布鲁斯|布魯士]]任命卡特摩尔為新隊長。但卡特摩尔於其頭三場比賽有兩場於上半場已領兩黃一紅被遂出場，而領隊向傳媒透露並沒有打算更換隊長<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/sep/15/sunderland |title='Distraught' Lee Cattermole still clinging on to Sunderland captaincy |publisher=''guardian.co.uk'' |date=2010-09-15 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2010-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100919015709/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/sep/15/sunderland |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2012年10月29日，[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]隊長卡特摩尔與球會簽四年新約留隊至2016年夏季<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20120328 |title=Lee Cattermole signs new Sunderland deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-10-29 |accessdate=2013-06-07 |archive-date=2012-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101073953/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20120328 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===國家隊===
卡特摩尔曾分別代表[[英格蘭16歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U16]]、[[英格蘭17歲以下足球代表隊|U17]]、[[英格蘭18歲以下足球代表隊|U18]]及[[英格蘭19歲以下足球代表隊|U19]]，於2003年首次代表U16在[[勝利盾|勝利盾]]（Victory Shield）對威爾斯U16<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.gazettelive.co.uk/boro-fc/boro-fc-news/tm_headline=boro-s-homegrown-heroes--lee-cattermole&method=full&objectid=17987895&siteid=109975-name_page.html |title=Lee Cattermole |publisher=gazettelive.co.uk |date=2006-10-25 |accessdate=2009-04-10 |archive-date=2009-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091227070741/http://www.gazettelive.co.uk/boro-fc/boro-fc-news/tm_headline%3Dboro-s-homegrown-heroes--lee-cattermole%26method%3Dfull%26objectid%3D17987895%26siteid%3D109975-name_page.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，更獲派擔任U19[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]之職<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11680_2399060,00.html |title=Cattermole eyes captaincy |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-12-18 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084855/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11680_2399060,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2006年9月29日卡特摩尔獲時任[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]主教練的[[彼得·泰勒|彼得·泰萊]]首次徵召入伍，備戰下月在[[2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]對德國U21的兩回合外圍賽附加賽，而[[加布里埃爾·阿格邦拉霍|艾邦拉荷]]亦同時首度入選<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2390871,00.html |title=Taylor names Under-21 squad |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-09-31 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084234/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_2390871,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。小國腳順利晉級，卡特摩尔入選在[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]舉行決賽週的30人初選名單<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6644497.stm |title=FA names 30-man England U21 squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-10 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610110520/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6644497.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但因傷落選最終23人大軍<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6702087.stm |title=Bentley picked for England U21s |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-30 |accessdate=2009-04-08 |archive-date=2007-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070920173114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6702087.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年6月1日卡達莫獲選進入英格蘭U21參加在[[瑞典|瑞典]]舉行[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]決賽週最後23人大軍名單，終於可以一嘗大賽滋味<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8070858.stm |title=England Under-21s hit by injuries |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-06-01 |accessdate=2009-06-09 |archive-date=2009-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601165338/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8070858.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。6月15日首戰芬蘭U21，卡達莫接應[[加布里埃爾·阿格邦拉霍|艾邦拉荷]]傳中射入先拔頭籌，協助大部分時間10人應戰的球隊險勝2-1完場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8099419.stm |title=England U21s 2-1 Finland U21s |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-06-15 |accessdate=2009-06-16 |archive-date=2009-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090616012807/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8099419.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年9月4日[[2011年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2011年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽作客首戰[[馬其頓21歲以下國家足球隊|馬其頓U21]]，在上屆比賽完結後，大部分主力成員超齡離隊，卡特摩尔成為隊中老大哥，獲委為[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/MatchCentre/2009/MacedoniaEngland/MatchPreviews/team_news_040909.aspx |title=Sturridge & Naughton start |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2009-09-04 |accessdate=2009-09-05 |archive-date=2009-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090908120822/http://thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/MatchCentre/2009/MacedoniaEngland/MatchPreviews/team_news_040909.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，不負所托，在完賽前射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]反超前2-1，協助球隊旗開得勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8238933.stm |title=Macedonia U21 1-2 England U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-09-04 |accessdate=2009-09-05 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206104051/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8238933.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

